scoringPlays.text: David Sills V 18 Yd pass from Will Grier (Evan Staley Kick)
Hakeem Butler 4 Yd pass from Brock Purdy (Connor Assalley Kick)
David Montgomery 2 Yd Run (Connor Assalley PAT failed)
Charlie Kolar 19 Yd pass from Brock Purdy (Connor Assalley Kick)
Derrek Pitts Jr. 72 Yd Return of Blocked Field Goal (Evan Staley Kick)
Deshaunte Jones 32 Yd pass from Brock Purdy (Brock Purdy Pass to Matthew Eaton for Two-Point Conversion)

videos.description: Will Grier goes up top and drops a dime to wide receiver David Stills V for the 18-yard TD.
videos.headline: Grier finds Stills for TD

videos.description: Iowa State quarterback Brock Purdy takes the hit and finds wide receiver Hakeem Butler for the 4-yard touchdown.
videos.headline: ISU QB takes hit and finds wide open WR for TD

videos.description: Iowa State running back David Montgomery follows his blocks and goes untouched into the end zone for the 2-yard touchdown run.
videos.headline: ISU RB walks into the end zone for TD

videos.description: Iowa State tight end Charlie Kolar catches it and is able to out run the defense for the 19-yard touchdown.
videos.headline: ISU TE makes the catch and turns up field for the TD

videos.description: Kenny Bigelow Jr. blocks the kick and Derrek Pitts Jr. picks it up and returns it 72 yards for the touchdown.
videos.headline: WVU blocks kick and returns it for TD

videos.description: Iowa State fans rush the field after their team upsets No. 6 West Virginia.
videos.headline: Iowa State fans can't be kept off the field
